-- TO create a npm package, 
1. Create a folder with the name of the package
2. Create a file with the name of the package 
 also u can use any desired name it u do that you have to specify the name in the package.json file
3. Create a package.json file


note;-(index.js is the entry point of the package)




import {someFIle} from 'name' --> (name is without the path and the extension)
 (the node will start searching for the package in the node_modules folder)
